IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
    PROGRAM-ID. AdvancedExample.
    AUTHOR. DataCenterTeam.
    VERSION. 0-2-0.

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
    OS "Linux".
    ARCH "x86_64".
    RUNTIME-VERSION "1.0".

DATA DIVISION.
    INPUT VIDEO-MP4 AS VIDEO-STREAM.
    INPUT AUDIO-WAV AS AUDIO-FEED.
    INPUT BINARY-BLOB AS BLOB.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    TRANSCODE VIDEO-STREAM IMAGE-JPG.
    FILTER AUDIO-FEED has_sound.
    MERGE VIDEO-STREAM,AUDIO-FEED INTO MIXED-STREAM.
    ENCRYPT BLOB.
    DECRYPT BLOB.
